    answer: "Reply once in any thread and the AI relinquishes the conversation permanently. Most EV installers let the AI gather the initial scope — vehicle model, charger preference, mounting position, cable run, supply type, and grant interest — then take over to discuss the specific electrical requirements and confirm the installation date."
